snippet.title: Stuck At Lv. 1 - Trailer
snippet.description:
https://donkay20.itch.io/stuck-at-lv-1

Stuck At Lv. 1 is a roguelike action RPG in which the player plays as a protagonist who is cursed and is unable to "level up" his vampiric abilities, and must work around this restriction. Explore the Vespera Realm, steal enemy attacks and find out the truth about your curse!
